Mobile Advertising:  To opt out of mobile advertising, you can visit your mobile device’s “settings” menu and adjust the device’s ad tracking settings (such as turning off the feature to “Allow Apps to Request to Track”). Certain apps, such as the Digital Advertising Alliance’s “AppChoices” app can help you exercise your behavioral advertising choices and are available from some platform providers (such as Apple or Google).  For more information, please see the “analytics & advertising” section above.
