any use or access to the Service by anyone under 18 is strictly prohibited and in violation of this Agreement. Our Services are not directed to, and we do not intend to, or knowingly, collect or solicit personal data from children under the age of 18. If you are under the age of 18, please do not use our websites or online services or otherwise provide us with any personal data either directly or by other means.
